Project Analysis
This is a Django-based VoIP/Telecommunications Management Platform with FreeSWITCH integration. Here's a comprehensive overview:

Core Purpose
Call Data Record (CDR) management and billing system for VoIP operations
Multi-tenant platform supporting businesses, clients, providers, and routing
Real-time call routing, trunk group management, and monitoring
Architecture
Database:

PostgreSQL backend with two databases:
ppdev: Main application database
ppcdr: Dedicated CDR (call records) database
Custom models for high-volume call tracking
Main Components:

pp - Django web application
arch - Shared application models and utilities
fs - FreeSWITCH integration layer
Key Modules
Module	Purpose
account/	User authentication, login/logout, help system
cdr/	Call detail records, billing analysis
routing/	Call routing, trunk groups, gateway management
business/	Business entity management
switch/	FreeSWITCH server management
e911/	Emergency services integration
graph/	Analytics and performance visualization
sms/	SMS messaging
chat/	Chat functionality
accounting/	Financial tracking and reporting
django_countries/	Country/region management
Workflow System
Multi-step workflow (Workflow1) for client setup: Client → Group → Gateway → DIDs
Guided setup process with form validation
Infrastructure Features
Server management scripts (start, stop, restart, status, logs)
Development server runs on 0.0.0.0:8000
Monitoring/ping system in ping for health checks
Real-time process monitoring with daemon support
Data Model Highlights
CDRs with financial tracking (currency fields, billing seconds)
Multi-level hierarchy: Client → Trunk Groups → DIDs (Direct Inward Dials)
Gateway management for provider connections
Historical logging and audit trails
Deployment
Development environment with Django manage.py
Shell scripts for server lifecycle management
Log rotation and monitoring capabilities
Cron-based maintenance (cronminute.sh)
This platform manages the complete lifecycle of VoIP calls for businesses—from intake through billing—with multi-tenant support and comprehensive reporting.
